499
00:53:22,880 --> 00:53:26,280
Oh! Another egg! Yes, yes!

500
00:53:41,080 --> 00:53:44,280
All right, you guys keep doing that.

501
00:53:56,080 --> 00:53:58,580
Oh, slow falling.

502
00:54:01,080 --> 00:54:03,480
