504
00:54:09,680 --> 00:54:11,880
more honey.

505
00:54:31,080 --> 00:54:34,880
Because even if we get like less rare bees, we can sell it.

506
00:54:35,080 --> 00:54:39,080
They do go for like 2,000, or like 500 and stuff.

507
00:55:08,588 --> 00:55:11,288
ね、ね、ねね、ねね。
Ne, ne, nene, nene.

508
00:55:23,088 --> 00:55:25,588
It's a mystery...

509
00:55:30,088 --> 00:55:33,588
あ、ななな...
Ah, na na na...

510
00:55:33,588 --> 00:55:42,588
うわ！ふふふ...
Whoa! *laughs*

511
00:55:42,588 --> 00:55:48,588
コードが壊れてる！
The code is broken!

512
00:55:48,588 --> 00:55:53,088
なんかサンタの声が聞こえた気がする。
I feel like I heard Santa's voice.

513
00:55:53,088 --> 00:55:59,588
Maybe I should invest in a diamond pickaxe. Or diamond axe, so it lasts a little longer.

514
00:55:59,588 --> 00:56:10,588
な、なな、な。
Na, nana, na.

515
00:56:10,588 --> 00:56:16,288
I guess the goal is to get a bee that gives me as much... Ah!

516
00:56:16,288 --> 00:56:20,088
