517
00:56:20,088 --> 00:56:24,088
All right, I'll be back for these pumpkins.

518
00:56:24,088 --> 00:56:28,088
ん、な、なな。
Mhm, na, nana.

519
00:56:28,088 --> 00:56:30,588
Got so many pumpkins.

520
00:56:38,088 --> 00:56:40,088
Oh, birch sapling.

521
00:56:40,088 --> 00:56:49,088
な、なな、な。
Na, nana, na.

522
00:56:49,088 --> 00:56:54,088
All right, any eggs? Oh, yes!

523
00:56:54,088 --> 00:56:56,588
I don't know...

524
00:56:56,588 --> 00:57:04,088
...for the number of family members here, there seems to be a lack of eggs. Please...

525
00:57:11,088 --> 00:57:14,088
Look at all those chickens.

526
00:57:14,088 --> 00:57:23,088
へへへ...
*giggles*

527
00:57:23,088 --> 00:57:27,088
Pie...

528
00:57:33,088 --> 00:57:38,088
Grow faster. Grow faster.

529
00:57:38,088 --> 00:57:44,088
Produce eggs.

530
00:57:44,088 --> 00:57:48,588
Where'd the string come from?

531
00:57:48,588 --> 00:58:03,088
ん、うーん...
Mhm, hmmm...

532
00:58:03,088 --> 00:58:08,588
We can sell these, actually, can't we?

533
00:58:08,588 --> 00:58:13,088
ふふ... Trying to be frugal here.
*giggles* Trying to be frugal here.

534
00:58:13,088 --> 00:58:22,088
Okay, we're gonna get a diamond axe, we'll grab one of those archaeological... oh...

535
00:58:22,088 --> 00:58:29,088
It's fine, I get it. You guys are a little shy to egg when I'm around.

536
00:58:29,088 --> 00:58:37,088
But I heard it. I heard you loud and clear. Okay.

537
00:58:37,088 --> 00:58:47,088
ね、ねね、ね。
Ne, nene, ne.

538
00:58:47,088 --> 00:58:52,088
Okay, we'll get one of the brushes, and we'll get a diamond axe.

539
00:58:52,088 --> 00:59:00,088
And then... so... then...

540
00:59:06,088 --> 00:59:09,088
Oh, slow falling. Whee! Whee!

541
00:59:09,088 --> 00:59:12,088
カブ、カブ。 カブ。
Turnip, turnip. Turnip.

542
00:59:12,088 --> 00:59:16,088
これもしかして、今アルケミストと...
Is this perhaps, right now with the Alchemist...

543
00:59:16,088 --> 00:59:22,088
ネコラボホールディングスする？
Are we doing Nekolabo Holdings?

544
00:59:22,088 --> 00:59:32,088
どうする、みんな？ 買っちゃったからな、４万持ってる。
What should we do, everyone? Since I bought it, I have 40,000.

545
00:59:32,088 --> 00:59:42,088
ノーマルはこれから出てくるし。 今日は合計６千万売買できるよね。
Normal ones will appear from now on. Today we can trade a total of 60 million, right.

546
00:59:42,088 --> 00:59:47,088
お、みこち、どこ行くの？
Oh, Mikochi, where are you going?

547
00:59:47,088 --> 00:59:52,088
カブなう！
Turnip now!

548
00:59:52,088 --> 00:59:54,088
Wait, wasn't cake...?

549
00:59:54,088 --> 00:59:59,088
Oh... oh...

550
01:00:00,396 --> 01:00:02,596
I don't need pumpkin for cake.

551
01:00:05,196 --> 01:00:06,396
Brush, brush.

552
01:00:10,196 --> 01:00:13,296
おら！カブの時間や！カブや！
Hey! It's turnip time! Turnips!

553
01:00:13,396 --> 01:00:15,596
20,000... たかい。
20,000... That's expensive.

554
01:00:20,496 --> 01:00:22,596
But it does last a long time.

555
01:00:35,496 --> 01:00:37,596
あったー！ | いえーい！
Found it! | Yay!

556
01:00:41,596 --> 01:00:45,596
ドロボウ建設... | 確かに、確かに。 | やめてね。
Robber Construction... | True, true. | Please don't.

557
01:00:47,396 --> 01:00:49,096
Dorobou Construction...
Robber Construction...

558
01:00:49,296 --> 01:00:51,596
おー！ハラサキさん！ | 34！
Oh! Harasaki-san! | 34!

559
01:00:53,596 --> 01:00:56,596
ハチカ？ | んな建設！
Hachika? | What kind of construction is that?!

560
01:01:04,596 --> 01:01:06,596
I wonder if I can go find some watermelon.

561
