お！プラス100%！ | おー！
Oh! Plus 100%! | Oh!

562
01:01:09,496 --> 01:01:11,896
90円。 | でも割れてんだよな。
90 yen. | But it's split.

563
01:01:11,896 --> 01:01:14,296
全部割れてんだな。
They're all split.

564
01:01:21,096 --> 01:01:23,596
We do have stocks. Why doesn't it show up in...

565
01:01:25,596 --> 01:01:27,596
