566
01:01:28,596 --> 01:01:31,596
Please, please, please. Please, please.

567
01:01:36,096 --> 01:01:38,596
My stocks... my stocks...

568
01:01:42,596 --> 01:01:45,596
No, we hold! We hold!

569
01:01:53,096 --> 01:01:55,596
Yeah, 100%...

570
01:01:55,596 --> 01:01:58,596
...だってもう...
...because...

571
01:02:01,596 --> 01:02:03,596
え？らーめん？
Eh? Ramen?

572
01:02:07,596 --> 01:02:10,596
どこから来た？このらーめん。
Where did this ramen come from?

573
01:02:13,596 --> 01:02:15,596
