574
01:02:21,096 --> 01:02:25,096
らーめん、らーめん...
Ramen, ramen...

575
01:02:33,296 --> 01:02:35,896
いや、なんかお腹空いた。
Yeah, I'm kind of hungry.

576
01:02:35,896 --> 01:02:37,596
お腹空いた。
I'm hungry.

577
01:02:40,596 --> 01:02:42,596
ご飯食べるの忘れた。
I forgot to eat food.

578
01:02:53,596 --> 01:02:57,596
らーめん、らーめん...
Ramen, ramen...

579
01:03:15,096 --> 01:03:17,596
Oh, we need more bees. Soon, soon.

580
01:03:18,596 --> 01:03:21,096
Oh right, I forgot to buy honey.

581
01:03:52,096 --> 01:03:54,096
Oh! Speed!

582
01:04:09,096 --> 01:04:12,596
It would be nice to find some watermelons.

583
01:04:12,596 --> 01:04:15,096
'Cause the melons grow so fast, and then you can get melon slices.

584
01:04:19,096 --> 01:04:21,296
I can replace the pumpkin with melon.

585
01:04:21,296 --> 01:04:23,596
But where would I find melon?

586
01:04:25,096 --> 01:04:28,096
Where would I find a melon?

587
01:04:35,096 --> 01:04:37,096
Jungle?

588
01:04:39,096 --> 01:04:42,596
Is there a jungle nearby? It would be nice.

589
01:05:04,304 --> 01:05:09,204
And then... this...

590
01:05:23,104 --> 01:05:27,604
Ha! Two eggs. Only two?

591
01:05:38,304 --> 01:05:40,904
Grow faster, children.

592
01:05:46,104 --> 01:05:50,604
I don't think they sell melon, no?

593
01:06:00,104 --> 01:06:03,604
Uh! Farm Money Boost! Yes! Yes, yes, yes.

594
01:06:21,104 --> 01:06:24,104
Oh, another.

595
01:06:43,604 --> 01:06:47,104
Okay, buy more honey.

596
01:06:52,104 --> 01:06:56,604
How much honey should I buy? Like 20? 40?

597
01:07:16,904 --> 01:07:20,604
But the boss... the boss is pretty easy.

598
01:07:20,604 --> 01:07:25,604
Okay, like, yeah, we have the shoes now.

599
01:07:25,604 --> 01:07:30,104
Yeah! Yeah! Yeah! You guys are so strong!

600
01:07:30,104 --> 01:07:34,604
Look at you! Look at you with your diamond... with your diamond shoes!

601
01:07:34,604 --> 01:07:37,104
He has the same outfit!

602
01:07:37,104 --> 01:07:40,104
Oh! It's matching! Matching!

603
01:07:40,104 --> 01:07:42,604
Matching shoes!

604
01:07:42,604 --> 01:07:44,304
Matching shoes!

605
01:07:44,304 --> 01:07:46,104
Matching shoes?

606
01:07:46,104 --> 01:07:48,104
Eh? Wait, Anya matches too!

607
01:07:48,104 --> 01:07:52,104
Matches! Matching!

608
01:07:52,104 --> 01:07:55,304
Matching shoes!

609
01:07:55,304 --> 01:07:58,304
Oh, this is so romantic.

610
01:07:58,304 --> 01:08:02,604
Ina, have you went to the dungeons or Nazotoki?

611
01:08:02,604 --> 01:08:04,604
Oh, not today.

612
01:08:04,604 --> 01:08:07,604
