613
01:08:07,604 --> 01:08:09,104
Farming.

614
01:08:09,104 --> 01:08:11,904
Farming?! Oh...

615
01:08:11,904 --> 01:08:14,304
You're so dedicated!

616
01:08:14,304 --> 01:08:16,904
Yeah. I adore you!

617
01:08:16,904 --> 01:08:20,604
Maybe, maybe you can spare a few bees?

618
01:08:20,604 --> 01:08:22,604
A bee or two?

619
01:08:22,604 --> 01:08:25,604
Um, not on me, though, unfortunately.

620
01:08:25,604 --> 01:08:29,104
Oh! You don't have any bees on you right now?

621
01:08:29,104 --> 01:08:30,904
Wait, how do you sell stuff?

622
01:08:30,904 --> 01:08:33,104
I have this, though. It's Koronesuki, right?

623
01:08:33,104 --> 01:08:34,604
From Santa.

624
01:08:34,604 --> 01:08:38,304
Whoa! Yellow also looks like... wait, you have that?

625
01:08:40,104 --> 01:08:42,104
Yeah!

626
01:08:42,104 --> 01:08:44,304
Wait, you too? You too, Mococo?

627
01:08:44,304 --> 01:08:46,604
Really?!

628
01:08:46,604 --> 01:08:50,104
We also both have Koronesuki!

629
01:08:50,104 --> 01:08:53,104
Oh! How? How did you get it?

630
01:08:53,104 --> 01:08:55,604
Can you...?

631
01:08:55,604 --> 01:08:58,104
You can get rid of the Koronesuki?

632
01:08:58,104 --> 01:09:02,904
I can also sell my Koronesuki for 1,000,000,000 Yen!

633
01:09:02,904 --> 01:09:05,604
Wait, did you guys get a Takodachi?

634
01:09:05,604 --> 01:09:07,604
Not yet.

635
01:09:07,604 --> 01:09:10,104
Oh... Can you sell the Koronesuki for it?

636
01:09:10,104 --> 01:09:11,904
I didn't... I didn't get it.

637
01:09:11,904 --> 01:09:15,604
I got that from Santa for being a good kid.

638
01:09:15,604 --> 01:09:18,104
Oh...

639
01:09:18,104 --> 01:09:20,604
Oh, and you're gonna sell it away?

640
01:09:20,604 --> 01:09:24,604
You're passing on the Christmas magic to us?

641
01:09:24,604 --> 01:09:26,604
Of course, of course!

642
01:09:26,604 --> 01:09:28,604
Spread the joy.

643
01:09:28,604 --> 01:09:30,304
Joy to the world!

644
01:09:30,304 --> 01:09:33,304
Joy to the world!

645
01:09:33,304 --> 01:09:36,604
Koronesuki to the world!

646
01:09:36,604 --> 01:09:38,304
Yeah!

647
01:09:42,604 --> 01:09:45,604
Ah, can we do it? Can we sell the Koronesuki?

648
01:09:45,604 --> 01:09:49,104
Don't sell it! That was a present!

649
01:09:49,104 --> 01:09:51,604
Oh, don't sell? Oh...

650
01:09:51,604 --> 01:09:53,104
Let's go, Mococo.

651
