652
01:10:11,112 --> 01:10:13,112
Is that where you use it?

653
01:10:14,312 --> 01:10:18,312
にゃにゃにゃにゃにゃ〜
Nya nya nya nya nya~

654
01:10:24,112 --> 01:10:25,612
Sand or gravel?

655
01:10:26,212 --> 01:10:28,112
Oh, we have some sand.

656
01:10:30,512 --> 01:10:33,312
Any chick- Any eggs?

657
01:10:36,212 --> 01:10:37,412
No eggs?

658
01:10:37,412 --> 01:10:39,912
Ah! No! No! No!

659
01:10:39,912 --> 01:10:41,312
What are you doing? What are you doing?

660
01:10:41,312 --> 01:10:44,312
Don't escape! Come back, I have seeds.

661
01:10:44,712 --> 01:10:47,412
What happened? How did they escape?

662
01:10:48,612 --> 01:10:50,912
Is there too many of them?

663
01:10:55,812 --> 01:10:57,712
What happened?

664
01:11:02,912 --> 01:11:05,212
やばい、やばい。
Oh boy. Oh boy.

665
01:11:30,112 --> 01:11:34,112
Alright, that should be good enough for now.

666
01:11:44,012 --> 01:11:45,412
Phew.

667
01:11:51,612 --> 01:11:53,112
That was close.

668
01:12:00,112 --> 01:12:04,312
I mean, we can dig on the ground and make a coop under- under- underground.

669
01:12:04,312 --> 01:12:05,612
That's an option.

670
01:12:07,612 --> 01:12:10,012
Maybe they are not happy with their working conditions.

671
01:12:45,612 --> 01:12:48,612
An honest farming here.

672
01:12:57,312 --> 01:12:58,612
Phew.

673
01:13:08,112 --> 01:13:09,612
Man, life is tough.

674
01:13:10,512 --> 01:13:13,312
Where are they gonna start a union? Hope not!

675
01:13:23,112 --> 01:13:24,612
I wonder what other skills...

676
01:13:25,112 --> 01:13:27,312
Forgot some spots.

677
01:13:29,112 --> 01:13:31,312
...what other skills the bees have?

678
01:13:47,112 --> 01:13:49,312
うーん…
Mmm...

679
01:13:56,612 --> 01:13:57,912
Okay.

680
01:14:02,112 --> 01:14:04,312
Maybe go search for a jungle?

681
01:14:04,312 --> 01:14:05,612
Ah...

682
01:14:06,112 --> 01:14:08,112
Maybe...

683
01:14:27,112 --> 01:14:29,112
I think we'll find some sand and stuff...

684
01:14:29,112 --> 01:14:31,612
...and do the alchemy.

685
01:14:31,612 --> 01:14:33,312
There's a little bit of sand over there.

686
01:14:42,912 --> 01:14:45,112
Any eggs?

687
01:14:45,612 --> 01:14:47,112
One?

688
01:14:50,112 --> 01:14:53,612
One single egg amongst all of you?!

689
01:15:00,220 --> 01:15:01,920
One single egg?

690
01:15:06,420 --> 01:15:07,820
You're slacking.

691
01:15:10,220 --> 01:15:12,820
Get two, three, four... Oh! Oh! Oh!

692
01:15:12,820 --> 01:15:15,120
Now we're talking.

693
01:15:17,420 --> 01:15:19,520
Now we're talking here.

694
01:15:27,620 --> 01:15:29,920
All right, all right.

695
01:15:36,620 --> 01:15:38,320
One more? Okay, okay, okay.

696
01:15:38,320 --> 01:15:41,620
Oh, I just don't have sugar. That's fine.

697
01:15:49,620 --> 01:15:51,620
All right, all right.

698
01:15:58,420 --> 01:15:59,820
狭い...
It's cramped...

699
01:16:00,720 --> 01:16:04,320
Well, well, well, working conditions, huh?

700
01:16:04,320 --> 01:16:07,020
Working conditions, huh?

701
01:16:10,020 --> 01:16:14,120
Oh, I guess I already have... I can break this shovel.

702
01:16:18,120 --> 01:16:21,120
Please, please, no pushing, no pushing.

703
01:16:24,820 --> 01:16:27,320
Trying to help us all here, okay?

704
01:16:31,320 --> 01:16:32,520
狭い...
It's cramped...

705
01:16:50,520 --> 01:16:52,820
Oh, please, oh, please.

706
01:17:02,620 --> 01:17:05,220
I'm trying to do you a favor here.

707
01:17:08,120 --> 01:17:10,020
Ah! Sorry!

708
01:17:31,220 --> 01:17:33,320
All right, all right.

709
01:17:43,820 --> 01:17:45,420
Yeah, leave that one.

710
01:17:47,820 --> 01:17:51,220
Excuse me, excuse me, excuse me!

711
01:18:01,120 --> 01:18:04,220
Excuse me, please get off the platform.

712
01:18:06,420 --> 01:18:10,620
Excuse me, off the platform, please.

713
01:18:11,920 --> 01:18:14,420
Off the platform!

714
01:18:14,820 --> 01:18:18,620
There we go. Ah, some peace.

715
01:18:50,520 --> 01:18:54,020
Oh, some eggs over there. I see it, I see it.

716
01:19:01,420 --> 01:19:04,920
I'm trying to help you guys here, okay?

717
01:19:04,920 --> 01:19:07,620
So you can live...

718
01:19:09,720 --> 01:19:12,220
...in a more broader space.

719
01:19:23,620 --> 01:19:25,620
Oh, there's a hole there.

720
01:19:29,720 --> 01:19:32,520
I need more wood. I guess I can use this.

721
01:19:57,520 --> 01:20:00,220
Maybe I should make ladders?

722
01:20:05,628 --> 01:20:08,128
Kind of efficient, though, but...

723
01:20:22,628 --> 01:20:25,628
Oh, now you start laying more eggs.

724
01:20:25,628 --> 01:20:27,628
Maybe it was a problem.

725
01:20:41,628 --> 01:20:43,628
Maybe they did need more space...

726
01:20:43,628 --> 01:20:47,128
...and a better working condition.

727
01:21:38,628 --> 01:21:42,628
I hope this is to your liking, chickens.

728
01:22:10,628 --> 01:22:15,628
Very cozy, thank you.

729
01:22:18,628 --> 01:22:21,128
Yes, yes.

730
01:22:25,628 --> 01:22:27,128
Nine eggs.

731
01:22:27,128 --> 01:22:31,628
I see an increase in production.

732
01:22:31,628 --> 01:22:35,128
I shall return again for a better yield...

733
01:22:35,128 --> 01:22:36,628
...next time.

734
01:22:40,128 --> 01:22:41,628
