High jumps.

1002
01:54:24,176 --> 01:54:25,676
Whee!

1003
01:54:28,676 --> 01:54:31,176
This wasn't the slow life I imagined.

1004
01:54:32,676 --> 01:54:35,676
I'm still very hungry.

1005
01:54:37,676 --> 01:54:39,176
パン売れる？
Can I sell bread?

1006
01:54:40,676 --> 01:54:44,176
100、200... ちょっと計算できない。300くらい。
100, 200... I can't calculate it. Around 300.

1007
01:54:44,676 --> 01:54:46,676
おおー！
Ooh!

1008
01:54:48,676 --> 01:54:50,676
パン要るのでは？
Don't we need bread?

1009
01:55:00,184 --> 01:55:02,684
美味しいパン... I haven't had bread in a while.
Delicious bread... I haven't had bread in a while.

1010
01:55:07,684 --> 01:55:09,684
Okay, sell all the carrots first.

1011
01:55:13,684 --> 01:55:15,184
ただいま。
I'm back!

1012
01:55:17,184 --> 01:55:18,684
このゴミどうしたら...
What should I do with this trash...

1013
01:55:19,684 --> 01:55:21,184
あ！イナちゃんだ！
Ah! It's Ina-chan!

1014
01:55:21,184 --> 01:55:22,684
あ、どうも。
Ah, hello.

1015
01:55:24,184 --> 01:55:28,684
タカミンはフリマでハチ売ったりしてる？ - いや、まだ...
Is Takamin selling bees at the flea market? - No, not yet...

1016
01:55:28,684 --> 01:55:32,184
どうなんだろうね。フリマ見るかな、みんな。
I wonder. Does everyone check the flea market?

1017
01:55:35,184 --> 01:55:39,684
結構なんかハチ2万5千円とかで売ってる人いたけどね。
Though there was someone selling bees for like 25,000 yen.

1018
01:55:39,684 --> 01:55:41,184
ね。
Right?

1019
01:55:43,184 --> 01:55:45,684
And wheat...

1020
01:55:54,184 --> 01:55:57,684
普通に売っちゃおうかな... 養蜂箱買って...
Maybe I should just sell them normally... Buy a beehive...

1021
01:55:57,684 --> 01:55:59,684
あ、ビビちゃん！ - はい！
Ah, Vivi-chan! - Yes!

1022
01:55:59,684 --> 01:56:03,184
ビビちゃん、フリマでハチ売ったりしてる？
Vivi-chan, are you selling bees at the flea market?

1023
01:56:03,184 --> 01:56:05,684
フリマでハチ売ってない。 - 売れるかな...
I'm not selling bees at the flea market. - I wonder if they'll sell...

1024
01:56:09,684 --> 01:56:11,684
すうごいファーマーの人たちだ。
What an amazing group of farmers.

1025
01:56:11,684 --> 01:56:13,684
そうそう... ハチをね...
That's right... The bees...

1026
01:56:13,684 --> 01:56:17,684
フリマで売るか、こっちで売るかどっちの方がいいんだろうって...
We're asking whether it's better to sell them at the flea market or here...

1027
01:56:17,684 --> 01:56:19,684
いやでもフリマちょっと買ってくれる人いなくないですか？
But aren't there not many people buying at the flea market?

1028
01:56:19,684 --> 01:56:21,184
そうなんです。
That's true.

1029
01:56:21,184 --> 01:56:25,184
あとハチが2万5千円とかで売れて...売れてて。
Also, bees are selling for like 25,000 yen...

1030
01:56:26,684 --> 01:56:30,184
2万5千円... 高いな。
25,000 yen... That's expensive.

1031
01:56:44,184 --> 01:56:50,184
Maybe I should leave some in the bank, cause what if I die, I will lose half of my money.

1032
01:56:51,684 --> 01:56:55,684
あ！え？え？なに？なに？
Ah! Eh? Eh? What? What?

1033
01:56:55,684 --> 01:56:57,184
Raid?

1034
01:57:02,184 --> 01:57:06,184
行こうよ！みこもまださん... ずっともう養蜂とさハチやってるんだけどこっちとらは。
Let's go! I've been doing beekeeping and bees this whole time over here.

1035
01:57:13,184 --> 01:57:15,684
I need to go buy... I need to buy a shield.

1036
01:57:15,684 --> 01:57:17,684
I don't wanna die.

1037
01:57:17,684 --> 01:57:19,684
ぷらぶるで... ぷらぶるいっぱい買っちゃったよ。
At Puraburu... I bought a lot of Puraburu.

1038
01:57:24,184 --> 01:57:29,184
いないいない、いいな... いないいないいいな... - AZKiちゃん。
Ina is not here, how nice... Ina is not here, how nice... - AZKi-chan.

1039
01:57:32,184 --> 01:57:35,684
AZKi-senpai is dangerous. The raid is coming.

1040
01:57:36,184 --> 01:57:38,184
来とる来とる！
It's coming, it's coming!

1041
01:57:40,184 --> 01:57:41,684
Raid? Raid?

1042
01:57:42,684 --> 01:57:44,684
Anya?

1043
01:57:44,684 --> 01:57:46,684
Is that... Anya?

1044
01:57:48,184 --> 01:57:51,684
Yeah, you see... you see the ominous...?

1045
01:57:51,684 --> 01:57:52,684
Yeah.

1046
01:57:52,684 --> 01:57:54,684
Can I hit you?

1047
01:57:55,684 --> 01:57:56,684
I know what's about to happen.

1048
01:57:56,684 --> 01:58:01,184
You're a fighter, right? Protect me! Protect this... weak farmer!

1049
01:58:02,684 --> 01:58:06,184
Who's weak? Look at you, fully geared.

1050
01:58:06,184 --> 01:58:08,684
No, I'm so weak.

1051
01:58:09,184 --> 01:58:10,684
No, you're not.

1052
01:58:10,684 --> 01:58:11,684
I'm so weak.

1053
01:58:11,684 --> 01:58:15,684
You're the legendary... legendary farmer, Ina... Ina, I've been your fan.

1054
01:58:15,684 --> 01:58:17,684
I'm a huge fan!

1055
01:58:18,684 --> 01:58:22,684
Yeah, I'm a huge fan of you.

1056
01:58:22,684 --> 01:58:24,184
Aww...

1057
01:58:24,684 --> 01:58:28,684
How do you... how do you keep yourself so dedicated to your farming?

1058
01:58:29,684 --> 01:58:31,684
Well... well...

1059
01:58:32,684 --> 01:58:36,684
Well, I do have a whole song about farming.

1060
01:58:36,684 --> 01:58:37,684
Oh?

1061
01:58:37,684 --> 01:58:40,184
Because farming is all about bees, right?

1062
01:58:40,184 --> 01:58:41,184
Yeah.

1063
01:58:41,184 --> 01:58:45,184
And then I have a song that goes "Ichi hachi..."

1064
01:58:49,184 --> 01:58:54,184
So, you know... to be a dedicated farmer, you need to have an entire original song dedicated to farming.

1065
01:58:54,184 --> 01:58:57,184
I want to be like you. How can I be like you?

1066
01:58:59,184 --> 01:59:05,684
Well, you can start by becoming a farmer, but fighter... fighter is good too. I had my origins as a fighter, as well.

1067
01:59:05,684 --> 01:59:09,684
What do I need to be a farmer like you?

1068
01:59:10,684 --> 01:59:11,684
Oh, you just need...

1069
01:59:11,684 --> 01:59:16,184
One hoe, and a dream. And maybe a seed.

1070
01:59:17,684 --> 01:59:19,684
Oh...

1071
01:59:19,684 --> 01:59:25,184
What do you... what do you do farming? I mean, obviously you guys farm, but like, is there like a place where you guys farm?

1072
01:59:26,184 --> 01:59:28,684
You just farm. Like Minecraft.

1073
01:59:29,684 --> 01:59:31,184
Yeah, where do you... where do you do it?

1074
01:59:31,184 --> 01:59:35,184
Just outside the town, anywhere. Anywhere. You can start anywhere.

1075
01:59:35,184 --> 01:59:41,184
Even if you have a tragic past, you can... you can set all that aside and you can have a new start in the farm.

1076
01:59:41,184 --> 01:59:44,184
Oh my god, you're right. You're right. Oh my god, eight seconds left!

1077
01:59:44,184 --> 01:59:45,184
The raid!

1078
01:59:45,184 --> 01:59:49,684
Protect me, Anya! Anya! Anya! I'm scared! I'm scared!

1079
01:59:51,684 --> 01:59:53,684
え、なにこれ？！
Wait, what's that?!

1080
01:59:53,684 --> 01:59:56,684
ハトタウルスが来た！
The Hatotaur is here!

1081
01:59:56,684 --> 01:59:58,684
怖い、怖い！
Scary, scary!

1082
02:00:00,192 --> 02:00:03,192
ラーメン食べるのがいい
It's better to eat ramen.

1083
02:00:03,192 --> 02:00:05,292
おらおらおらおら！いけそういけそう！
Ora ora ora ora! Looks like we can do it!

1084
02:00:05,292 --> 02:00:08,692
おらおらおらおら！
Ora ora ora ora!

1085
02:00:10,192 --> 02:00:14,692
おらおらおらおら！
Ora ora ora ora!

1086
02:00:15,692 --> 02:00:18,692
おいおいおいおいおい！
Oi oi oi oi oi!

1087
02:00:18,692 --> 02:00:21,192
おいおいおいおい！
Oi oi oi oi!

1088
02:00:21,992 --> 02:00:23,192
ええええ？
Ehhhh?

1089
02:00:23,192 --> 02:00:26,692
フレンドリーファイアあります？
Is there friendly fire?

1090
02:00:27,692 --> 02:00:29,692
やばい！
Oh no!

1091
02:00:29,692 --> 02:00:32,192
フレンドリーファイア...
Friendly fire...

1092
02:00:35,192 --> 02:00:37,692
It's friendly fire!

1093
02:00:37,692 --> 02:00:40,192
ひっせー！
Watch out!

1094
02:00:41,692 --> 02:00:45,692
ファイターの一撃で誰かを殺害する可能性がある
There's a chance a Fighter's blow might kill someone.

1095
02:00:47,192 --> 02:00:50,692
おら！おら！
Ora! Ora!

1096
02:00:52,692 --> 02:00:54,692
痛い痛い痛い！
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

1097
02:00:54,692 --> 02:00:56,692
人殺しそうだよね
Seems like they're gonna kill someone.

1098
02:00:56,692 --> 02:00:59,192
あー！
Aaah!

1099
02:00:59,192 --> 02:01:03,192
味方、最悪だけど殴りやすいな
Teammates are the worst, but they're easy to hit.

1100
02:01:03,192 --> 02:01:05,692
おいおい！
Oi oi!

1101
02:01:12,692 --> 02:01:14,692
おら！
Ora!

1102
02:01:17,692 --> 02:01:20,692
おらおら！
Ora ora!

1103
02:01:21,192 --> 02:01:23,192
やばい、動けん
Oh no, I can't move!

1104
02:01:30,192 --> 02:01:33,392
Probably shouldn't have potato salad.

1105
02:01:33,392 --> 02:01:36,692
Yeah, we got an onigiri and about 5 different bread.

1106
02:01:36,692 --> 02:01:38,392
Some of us are just laughing and getting hit...

1107
02:01:38,392 --> 02:01:41,192
...by the members more than the boss!

1108
02:01:43,192 --> 02:01:45,192
おお！
Oooh!

1109
02:01:45,192 --> 02:01:47,192
踊り上手！
Good dancer!

1110
02:01:47,192 --> 02:01:49,192
何、何、何？
What, what, what?

1111
02:01:49,192 --> 02:01:52,192
狙われてる、動けた！
I'm targeted, I can move!

1112
02:01:53,192 --> 02:01:56,692
死んじゃう、死んじゃう
I'm gonna die, I'm gonna die!

1113
02:01:56,692 --> 02:01:58,692
面白いから
Because it's funny.

1114
02:01:58,692 --> 02:02:00,192
命が！うっせぇ！
My life! Shut up!

1115
02:02:00,192 --> 02:02:03,692
おっ、命が、命が...
Oh, my life, my life...

1116
02:02:03,692 --> 02:02:07,692
頑張れ、頑張れ！
Hang in there, hang in there!

1117
02:02:08,192 --> 02:02:11,192
ファイターの人倒したら、めっちゃもらえるの？
If we defeat the Fighter, do we get a lot?

1118
02:02:11,192 --> 02:02:15,692
ファイターの人、えい！えい！
Fighter, take this! Take this!

1119
02:02:15,692 --> 02:02:17,692
おらおらおらおら！
Ora ora ora ora!

1120
02:02:19,692 --> 02:02:22,192
やばいやばいやばい！
Oh no, oh no, oh no!

1121
02:02:22,192 --> 02:02:24,192
頑張れ！死んじゃう！
Hang in there, I'm gonna die!

1122
02:02:24,192 --> 02:02:26,692
おおおー！
Oooooh!

1123
02:02:32,192 --> 02:02:35,192
よいしょ！おらおらおらおら！
Heave-ho! Ora ora ora ora!

1124
02:02:35,192 --> 02:02:37,692
もうちょい！もうちょっとだ！
A bit more! Almost there!

1125
02:02:38,192 --> 02:02:40,692
おらおら！
Ora ora!

1126
02:02:45,192 --> 02:02:49,192
おらおらおらおら！
Ora ora ora ora!

1127
02:02:49,192 --> 02:02:53,192
おらおらおらおら！
Ora ora ora ora!

1128
02:02:54,192 --> 02:02:57,192
Yay!

1129
02:02:58,192 --> 02:03:00,192
びび、びび？
Bibi, Bibi?

1130
02:03:00,192 --> 02:03:02,192
びびちゃん？
Bibi-chan?

1131
02:03:02,192 --> 02:03:04,192
やったー！
We did it!

1132
02:03:04,192 --> 02:03:07,192
うれしいー！
So happy!

1133
02:03:07,192 --> 02:03:10,192
報酬、報酬ある？
Reward, is there a reward?

1134
02:03:10,192 --> 02:03:12,192
報酬ないの？
No reward?

1135
02:03:12,192 --> 02:03:14,192
報酬ないの、これ？
No reward for this?

1136
02:03:14,192 --> 02:03:17,192
報酬、何もないな
Reward, there's nothing.

1137
02:03:17,192 --> 02:03:20,192
びび！殺された、うさぎさんに！
Bibi! I was killed, by the rabbit!

1138
02:03:20,192 --> 02:03:22,192
びび大丈夫か？
Bibi, are you okay?

1139
02:03:22,192 --> 02:03:24,192
なーんだ、守っただけ？
Aw, man, we just defended?

1140
02:03:27,192 --> 02:03:29,192
I love how you were like...

1141
02:03:29,192 --> 02:03:32,192
...right as the second wave, or the enemy appears...

1142
02:03:32,192 --> 02:03:35,192
...you just ran?

1143
02:03:35,192 --> 02:03:38,392
Sorry, my... my Fighter blood, it... it called to me!

1144
02:03:41,192 --> 02:03:44,392
That was so funny, like...

1145
02:03:44,392 --> 02:03:46,192
何があったんですか？
What happened?

1146
02:03:46,192 --> 02:03:48,692
何が起きた？
What happened?

1147
02:03:48,692 --> 02:03:52,192
I'm sorry, "there's an enemy, I must defeat them!"

1148
02:03:52,192 --> 02:03:54,192
I was like, "Oh, I got teleported, and I must fight."

1149
02:03:56,192 --> 02:03:58,692
みなさん、おめでとうございます！
Everyone, congratulations!

1150
02:04:02,192 --> 02:04:04,192
えっとですね...
Well...

1151
02:04:04,192 --> 02:04:06,192
みなさん、あの...
Everyone, um...

1152
02:04:06,192 --> 02:04:09,192
あの、ハトタウロスおめでとうございます！
Um, congratulations on Hatotaur!

1153
02:04:09,192 --> 02:04:14,692
はい、えっと、無事倒せた皆さんにちょっとご褒美がございます！
Yes, well, we have a little reward for everyone who successfully defeated it!

1154
02:04:15,192 --> 02:04:18,692
おー！やったー！
Oh! We did it!

1155
02:04:20,192 --> 02:04:23,692
うちらがいない間に何か終わってたんだ
Something ended while we weren't here?

1156
02:04:24,192 --> 02:04:26,692
逆じゃね？入ってない
Isn't that the opposite? It's not in.

1157
02:04:27,192 --> 02:04:29,692
大丈夫です。皆さんに効果あるんで
It's okay, it affects everyone.

1158
02:04:30,192 --> 02:04:31,692
えっ、いいの？
Oh, is it okay?

1159
02:04:31,692 --> 02:04:34,192
何ですか何ですか？
What is it, what is it?

1160
02:04:34,192 --> 02:04:38,692
えっと、レイドを無事クリアできたので、
Well, since we successfully cleared the raid,

1161
02:04:38,692 --> 02:04:43,692
次の今から回すカブシルーレットが、特別版になります！
the next turn on the Stock Roulette we're about to spin will be a special edition!

1162
02:04:44,192 --> 02:04:48,192
おおー！
Oooooh!

1163
02:04:50,192 --> 02:04:52,192
今からじゃあカブ回すか。10時台の。
Shall we spin the stock now? The 10 o'clock one.

1164
02:04:52,192 --> 02:04:54,192
今、はい、今カブ回しますね。
Now, yes, I'm going to spin the stock now.

1165
02:04:54,192 --> 02:04:57,192
おおー！
Oooooh!

1166
02:05:00,200 --> 02:05:03,400
ネポラボホールディングス、いけー！
NePoLaBo Holdings, go!

1167
02:05:03,400 --> 02:05:07,200
最近やばかったね / わくわく
Lately, it's been crazy, hasn't it? / I'm so excited!

1168
02:05:07,200 --> 02:05:15,200
ということで、特別版ルーレットになります。
So, this is the special version roulette!

1169
02:05:15,200 --> 02:05:20,200
特別版ということで、良いのになってるんじゃないですか？
Since it's a special version, it should be good, right?

1170
02:05:20,200 --> 02:05:25,200
ししろんフーズ、ピー！
Shishiro Foods, spin!

1171
02:05:25,200 --> 02:05:32,200
え？ ゼロしかない？ / ゼロしかないじゃんこれ！
Wait, are there only zeros? / There are only zeros on this!

1172
02:05:33,200 --> 02:05:39,200
プラス50円！
Plus 50 yen!

1173
02:05:39,200 --> 02:05:46,200
ドロボウです！ / がんばれがんばれ！
Next is Dorobou! / Go, go!

1174
02:05:46,200 --> 02:05:54,200
あれ？お？
Oh? Huh?

1175
02:05:54,200 --> 02:06:00,200
プラス75円！
Plus 75 yen!

1176
02:06:00,200 --> 02:06:08,200
えー、ウナ電鉄！
Next, Una Railway!

1177
02:06:08,200 --> 02:06:14,200
プラス100円！
Plus 100 yen!

1178
02:06:14,200 --> 02:06:21,200
あ、ごめん、間違えたこれ。
Ah, sorry, I made a mistake.

1179
02:06:21,200 --> 02:06:29,200
これ、ウナ電鉄の次、大空なんだけど、ごめん、間違えた！
After Una Railway is Oozora, but sorry, I made a mistake!

1180
02:06:29,200 --> 02:06:38,200
大空を105円に戻してからやらせていただきますね。
I'll put Oozora back to 105 yen and spin again.

1181
02:06:38,200 --> 02:06:50,200
ちょっと大空は後で回すんで、ちょっとお待ちください。
I'll spin Oozora later, so please wait a bit.

1182
02:06:50,200 --> 02:06:59,200
先にネポラボ回しますね。
First, let's spin NePoLaBo.

1183
02:06:59,200 --> 02:07:07,200
100！100！100！ / プラス100円！
100! 100! 100! / Plus 100 yen!

1184
02:07:07,200 --> 02:07:18,200
Oh my god! 100! Plus 100!

1185
02:07:18,200 --> 02:07:24,200
ネポラボ... Sell.
NePoLaBo... Sell.

1186
02:07:24,200 --> 02:07:30,200
うわ、もう2000いけたんだ。
Oh, I could've sold 2000 more.

1187
02:07:30,200 --> 02:07:38,200
Whoa! Sold!

1188
02:07:38,200 --> 02:07:44,200
4000持ってるの？
You had 4000 shares?

1189
02:07:44,200 --> 02:07:51,200
Daily trading limit reached... Oh, what to do?

1190
02:07:51,200 --> 02:08:00,200
うわー、どうしようかな。
Wow, what should I do?

1191
02:08:00,200 --> 02:08:10,200
買い増しとこうかな。
Maybe I should buy more?

1192
02:08:40,200 --> 02:08:52,200
Now what...

1193
02:08:52,200 --> 02:09:00,200
Let's deposit 400,000.

1194
02:09:00,200 --> 02:09:15,200
Maybe I should buy a... what was it? / Withdraw 30,000.

1195
02:09:15,200 --> 02:09:24,200
Farmer... Shop. Wait, I'm going to...

1196
02:09:24,200 --> 02:09:31,200
Fine, let's just buy one.

1197
02:09:31,200 --> 02:09:45,200
売りました。Whew...
I sold them. Whew...

1198
02:10:00,508 --> 02:10:02,708
あくちゅ、ごめん...
Achoo! Sorry...

1199
02:10:14,508 --> 02:10:17,008
