1621
03:16:55,312 --> 03:16:59,312
Okay, I might make a short stop to sell some stuff.

1622
03:17:01,812 --> 03:17:05,812
Like the pie, the cooked cod...

1623
03:17:12,112 --> 03:17:14,312
Ooh!

1624
03:17:19,312 --> 03:17:22,812
Right now we can get you and you...

1625
03:17:24,312 --> 03:17:27,812
...get that going.

1626
03:17:29,812 --> 03:17:32,312
And another round of...

1627
03:17:32,312 --> 03:17:34,812
...carrots.

1628
03:17:51,812 --> 03:17:53,312
Ah, harvest.

1629
