It does end up being quite a bit of money, just needs some active grinding.

1650
03:20:32,820 --> 03:20:35,520
Like, I can do a thing where I just...

1651
03:20:35,520 --> 03:20:37,820
...keep only...

1652
03:20:40,820 --> 03:20:43,320
