Now, that's the pumpkin strat, is to have a pumpkin field so big, that once you make one round, it... the beginning has already regrown.

1668
03:23:24,820 --> 03:23:31,320
So then, you just endlessly farm pumpkins.

1669
03:23:45,120 --> 03:23:47,820
Did I pick that up first? Guess I did.

1670
03:23:52,320 --> 03:23:53,320
Whoops.

1671
03:24:14,820 --> 03:24:15,820
Oh wait.

1672
03:24:18,820 --> 03:24:21,320
Carrots, ca- ca- carrots.

1673
03:24:31,320 --> 03:24:32,320
Okay.

